          <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> (gear icon in bottom navigation).</li>
          <li>Scroll to the <strong>Account</strong> section.</li>
          <li>Tap <strong>"Delete Account"</strong>.</li>
          <li>Confirm the deletion in the dialog that appears.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Email Deletion Request</h2>
        <p>If you cannot access the app, you can request account deletion by emailing:</p>
