        <p>Include the email address associated with your account. We will process your request within 7 business days.</p>

        <h2>What Gets Deleted</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>âœ… Your profile information (name, email, avatar)</li>
          <li>âœ… All meeting transcriptions and summaries</li>
          <li>âœ… AI-generated insights and action items</li>
