          <li><strong>This action is permanent</strong> and cannot be undone.</li>
          <li>Data deletion is completed within <strong>30 days</strong> of the request.</li>
          <li>If you have an active Pro subscription, please cancel it separately through the App Store or Google Play to avoid future charges.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer t={t} locale="es" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-3xl); }
  .legal-content { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-xl); }
  .legal-content h1 { font-size: var(--fs-h1); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); background: var(--accent-gradient); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
  .legal-date { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: var(--fs-body); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .legal-content h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h2); font-weight: 700; margin-top: var(--space-lg); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-content p, .legal-content li { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-content ul, .legal-content ol { padding-left: var(--space-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-content li { margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
  .legal-content a { color: var(--accent-cyan); }
</style>
